  <tr class="en"> <td>
      Who arrived first?
  </td> </tr>
</table>
<li>
<table class="sentence" border=0>
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{suhitotenpuratodochira<strong>ga</strong>@KJ{{fond}}kidesuka.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      Which do you like better, sushi or tempura?
  </td> </tr>
</table>
<li>
<table class="sentence" border=0>
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{@KJ{{before^week^private}}<strong>ga</strong>@KJ{{see}}ta@KJ{{reflect^brush-stroke}}hatsumaranakatta.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      The film I saw last week was broing.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
<li>
<table class="sentence" border=0>
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{naze@KJ{{he}}<strong>ga</strong>sonnnakotowoyattaka, wakarimasenn.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      I don't know why he did something like that.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
<li>
<table class="sentence" border=0>
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{@KJ{{mother}}<strong>ga</strong>@KJ{{day^book}}nikuru@KJ{{in*front}}ni, kono@KJ{{section^roof}}wokireini
      @KJ{{sweep^exclude}}shinakereba naranai.}}
  </td> </tr>
