      Before my mother comes to Japan I have to make this room nice and clean.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
<li>
<table class="sentence" border=0>
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{@KJ{{africa^section}}sanha @KT{{gorufu}}<strong>ga</strong> dekimasu.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      Abe can play golf.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
<li>
<table class="sentence" border=0>
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{kokokara@KJ{{wealth^gentleman^mountain}}<strong>ga</strong>@KJ{{see}}emasu.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
